breakingChangesNotes:
In the commands gsuite-custom-user-schema-create and gsuite-custom-user-schema-update the argument 'field_json_entry_id' is getting an entry ID and will read the content of the json file in this entry id.
 In the command gsuite-datatransfer-request-create the argument 'applications_raw_json_entry_id' is getting an entry ID and will read the content of the json file in this entry id.
